data.description: Welcome home to the Community of Tapestry! This 2 story home features 4 bedrooms upstairs including a master bedroom suite with a spacious master bathroom, a shower and separate large soaking tub. Also a walk in closet! The kitchen has granite countertops, plenty of counter and cabinet space, with a large pantry. Fresh paint and new carpet. Seller is offering buydown rates with his preferred lender from 10/31/2023- 11/30/2023, all the way down to 5.5%. CALL US TODAY AND ASK US ABOUT LENDER’S BONUS AS WELL
